snippet.title: Hover Junkers "Outlaw" Trailer
snippet.description:
Purchase on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/380220/

Hover Junkers is a multiplayer virtual reality shooter where you scour the wasteland for loot while fighting off other junkers. Using motion tracked controllers and headset you aim, duck, and dodge to out maneuver and out gun your opponents.

Watch development every weekday at http://www.twitch.tv/stresslevelzero and join discussions or ask questions at http://www.reddit.com/r/hoverjunkers

You can get your own professionally built custom gaming PC at,
http://www.originpc.com/

https://twitter.com/brandonjla
https://twitter.com/stresslevelzero
